Emily Shearman (amụrụ n'abali iri abụo na atọ nke ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 1999) bụ onye na-agba egwuregwu ịnyịnya ígwè na New Zealand
Ọ nọchitere anya mba ya na egwuregwu  Commonwealth nke afọ 2022, ma rite ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ịchụso otu.
O sonyere  asọmpi iko mba ụwa nke afọ 2019/2020 , na asọmpi Oceania nke afọ 2019/-2020
Àtụ:2022 New Zealand Commonwealth Games team
